modName: Gammag33k's Thick-Fit BodySlide preset for UUNP-7B
summary: A basic preset for UUNP BodySlide based on the 7Base Bombshell model
descriptionHtml:
This is just a tweaked version of the UUNP - 7b Bombshell model that I like to use. I am kinda new to UUNP but I feel like UUNP presets don't give enough love to the booty. This preset looks really good with Pure Skin "sporty" mesh.

Enjoy!
